{"id":440316,"date":[{"year":1963,"month":2,"day":10}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"490","ytitle":"","mtitle":"五台山之歌","ftitle":"","authors":["郁群"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"郁群"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国建设要木材!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义要木材!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五台山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你听见了吗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你伸出翠绿的手来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向伟大的祖国献宝!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林业工人奔向五台山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑着树苗向前跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍峨的五台山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有多少高?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“初一滚下山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月半到山脚!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好!决心开山一辈子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滖上半月不算高；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滖到了山脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再向山顶跑!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林业工人奔到五台山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱着树苗向上跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茫茫的五台山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上山大路走哪条?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“上山没有路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万年长满草!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不!革命大路在脚下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕野草比人高；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万年长草的穷山窠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天也要向前跃!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人们披上麻袋衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥动了开路的刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻进野草人不见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造林歌声处处飘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声中间出现了路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背后跟来了绿树苗!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，豪迈的林场成立了:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍倒的野草盖成屋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踢开的乱石放鞭炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一批小树来祝贺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精神饱满站得齐又牢!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人们抱着树苗来宣誓:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们要把自己的青春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染绿社会主义的树苗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要和树苗一起成长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给未来的工厂、楼房、铁道……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一排人，万棵苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过了冬天向春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一步都把汗水浇；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一排人，万棵苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从山脚排到山顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从深谷插到云霄!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"观日台上红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五台山乐得哈哈笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它伸出了千万只翠绿的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着工人们向祖国来献宝:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“呵，祖国!木材，这里有!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五台出上的英雄们——才是真正的宝!”"}]}